data.title: Haitham Zein
data.meta_description: Haitham Ali Mohamad Al Haj Ali Zein, or simply Haitham Zein, is a Lebanese former footballer who played as a forward. He played for numerous Lebanese Premier League clubs, mainly at Tadamon Sour, and represented Lebanon internationally.
